sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Host as MCP host
    participant Client as MCP client
    participant Server as Notes server
    participant Store as NoteStore
    participant Disk as Notes workspace

    User->>Host: Ask about a note
    Host->>Client: Select read_note
    Client->>Server: Invoke with filename
    Server->>Store: read_note(filename)
    Store->>Store: Validate and resolve path
    alt Safe path
        Store->>Disk: Read Markdown
        Disk-->>Store: UTF-8 content
        Store-->>Server: NoteContent
        Server-->>Client: Structured tool result
        Client-->>Host: Add result to context
        Host-->>User: Answer
    else Unsafe path
        Store-->>Server: UnsafePathError
        Server-->>Client: Tool error
        Client-->>Host: Surface failure
    end
